 {"title": "Product Launch Readiness Certification", "description": "Before a major product launch, the enablement team builds a certification track in Mindtickle covering the new product's value proposition, target buyer profile, pricing model, and competitive positioning. The certification includes video lessons, written assessments, and two AI role-play scenarios: a discovery call with the target persona and an objection handling session. Reps must score 80% or higher to be certified to sell the new product. Of 200 AEs, 187 achieved certification within two weeks of launch. First-quarter new product revenue exceeded target by 14%."},
