 {"question": "Is Mindtickle worth it for teams under 50 reps?", "answer": "It depends on your enablement maturity. Teams with a dedicated enablement person who can build and maintain content will get value from Mindtickle at any team size. Teams without enablement resources often find the platform too heavy and would be better served by simpler tools like SalesHood or Gong's built-in coaching. The per-user economics improve at 50+ seats."},
